scenes.description: Opening 3D showcase title card and panning shots of Amelia Watson's 3D detective office.
Amelia Watson sits at her desk, introduces her 3D debut, spins in her chair, and looks at pictures of other Hololive members.
Amelia gets up from her chair and walks around the office, with the camera focus shifting to her movement and the room's details.

subtitles.original: Hello, everybody!
subtitles.english: Hello, everybody!

subtitles.original: Welcome to my 3D debut!
subtitles.english: Welcome to my 3D debut!

subtitles.original: Oh god, what year is it? Where am I?
subtitles.english: Oh god, what year is it? Where am I?

subtitles.original: Well, we're here in my office. Hello, everyone!
subtitles.english: Well, we're here in my office. Hello, everyone!

subtitles.original: Hi!
subtitles.english: Hi!

subtitles.original: Whee!
subtitles.english: Whee!

subtitles.english: Kyuu! Yoh! Ta-da!

subtitles.english: Just, you know, just hanging around. Just chillin'.
